title: Most popular online dating services in selected countries as of February 2014
summary: This grouped bar chart shows Percentage of respondents on the Y-axis for 9 different Countrys for 6 groups Facebook, Twitter, MySpace, Shaadi, Match, and Badoo that are presented on the X-axis.
Country Vietnam had the maximum Percentage of respondents among all 6 groups, and it was for Facebook. The minimum Percentage of respondents was observed in Country India for MySpace.
Among all the Countrys, Shaadi had the highest Percentage of respondents 14.0 in Country India and lowest value 0.0 in Country Indonesia.
There is a gap of 14.0 between the highest and lowest Percentage of respondents found for Shaadi in Country India and Indonesia.

max_summary: This grouped bar chart shows Percentage of respondents on the Y-axis for 9 different Countrys for 6 groups Facebook, Twitter, MySpace, Shaadi, Match, and Badoo that are presented on the X-axis.
Out of all 6 groups, Facebook had the highest Percentage of respondents in Country Vietnam and MySpace had the lowest Percentage of respondents in Country India.
In Country India, Shaadi had the highest Percentage of respondents among all 9 Countrys and it has the lowest Percentage of respondents in Country Indonesia.
Country India and Indonesia had the biggest gap of 14.0 between the highest and lowest Percentage of respondents found for Shaadi.
Among all 6 groups, Facebook had the gap of 36.0 between the maximum and minimum Percentage of respondents observed in Country Vietnam and Brazil respectively.
Facebook had the maximum Percentage of respondents out of all 6 groups in Country Vietnam followed by Facebook in Vietnam, and the minimum Percentage of respondents is found for MySpace in India.

On average, the Country Indonesia had the highest Percentage of respondents for all 6 groups Facebook, Twitter, MySpace, Shaadi, Match, and Badoo. Whereas Brazil had the lowest average Percentage of respondents.
